MS Nascom BASIC for Bemu80
==========================

This folder contains modified Microsoft (Nascom) BASIC 4.7 for the Bemu80 emulator.

This code is originally downloaded from http://searle.wales/z80/SimpleZ80.html (56k version),
and modified to work with the Bemu80 emulator.

Modifications
=============

The following modifications have been made to the Grant Searle's version of BASIC 4.7:

- Character input in `int.asm`
- Character output in `int.asm`
- ANSI clear screen in `int.asm` and `basic.asm`
- Set CR(carriage return) to 0x0A to match Enter key in `int.asm` and `basic.asm`

Copyright
=========

